     (patt_free_evar x ---> ‚ä• ---> ‚ä•)
     (Modus_ponens ‚àÖ (‚ä• ---> ‚ä• ---> ‚ä•) (‚ä• ---> ‚ä•)

        (Modus_ponens ‚àÖ (‚ä• ---> (‚ä• ---> ‚ä•) ---> ‚ä•)

Œ£: Signature

H: Œì ‚ä¢i exists_quantify x (evar_open 0 x P) ---> Q
using i
((ex , P) ---> Q) =
(exists_quantify x (evar_open 0 x P) ---> Q)

abstract (
  unfold exists_quantify;
  rewrite -> evar_quantify_evar_open by assumption;
  reflexivity
).

using i
(P ---> (ex , Q)) =
(P ---> exists_quantify x (evar_open 0 x Q))

abstract (
  unfold exists_quantify;
  rewrite -> evar_quantify_evar_open by assumption;
  reflexivity
).
Defined.


(* prenex-exists-and-left *)
